WEBVTT

00:00:00.746 --> 00:00:03.373
Today, I want to talk to you about dreams.

00:00:03.999 --> 00:00:06.716
I have been a lucid dreamer my whole life,

00:00:06.740 --> 00:00:08.716
and it's cooler than in the movies.

00:00:08.740 --> 00:00:10.683
(Laughter)

00:00:10.707 --> 00:00:13.415
Beyond flying, breathing fire,

00:00:13.439 --> 00:00:16.280
and making hot men
spontaneously appear ...

00:00:16.304 --> 00:00:18.281
(Laughter)

00:00:18.305 --> 00:00:20.713
I can do things like read and write music.

00:00:21.344 --> 00:00:24.675
Fun fact is that I wrote
my personal statement to college

00:00:24.699 --> 00:00:26.019
in a dream.

00:00:26.043 --> 00:00:28.798
And I did accepted. So, yeah.

00:00:29.873 --> 00:00:31.679
I am a very visual thinker.